    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The exterior looks great overall, though you will find some minor stone chips on the hood and a few light surface scratches consistent with careful regular use. Mechanically, the car is solid, starts reliably, and shifts smoothly, with all major systems functioning as intended. The interior is clean and comfortable, showing only light wear on the driver's seat bolster and floor mats. It\u2019s a dependable, attractive vehicle that is ready for its next owner without needing immediate major repairs.",
