    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this superlative example, maintained to an exacting standard that mirrors its original showroom delivery. The exterior retains a deep, mirror-like luster, while the interior remains entirely free of wear, reflecting a history of meticulous stewardship. This vehicle is mechanically indistinguishable from new and represents a premier acquisition for the connoisseur who demands uncompromising quality and aesthetic perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
