    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a pristine 1994 Mazda RX-7 (FD3S) featuring the legendary 13B-REW twin-rotor powerplant. This chassis retains its factory-spec sequential turbocharging system, delivering linear power delivery across the rev range with minimal boost threshold delay. The engine has undergone a comprehensive health check, showing exceptional compression across all rotor faces. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 5-speed manual transmission and a Torsen limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The suspension geometry remains true to its original double-wishbone design, providing unparalleled tactile feedback and cornering poise. This example is mechanically flawless, with zero vacuum leaks and a factory-spec cooling system. It is a turn-key collector-grade machine for the discerning enthusiast who demands peak performance and structural integrity.",
